Shell Says Ormen Lange Gas Field Production Halted Today

-- B y   B e n   F a r e y
-- 
2011-02-11T09:18:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-11/shell-says-ormen-lange-gas-field-off-norway-halted-production-today.html
  Royal Dutch Shell Plc  said natural-
gas production from its Ormen Lange field off  Norway ’s coast
halted today because of a “technical problem.”  “We are trying to restore production from Ormen Lange as
soon as possible,” Kim Blomley, a company spokesman, said by
telephone from The Hague.  To contact the reporter on this story:
